<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
The saving the cleric example keeps comming up when people defend the usefulness of Amnesia.  Amnesia is almost never the right answer.  Resist rate is too high on purples to be reliable, it causes unexpected agro shifts, agro will <B>not</B> shift to a tank, it will shift to either a high damage low armor class or another healer.  Amnesia in PvE has extremely limited application, and I would argue that your better off without it all together.<P>Edit:  Amnesia will never be fixed in the way that Bullseye describes.  It would become rediculiously overpowered.<P>Syth
</FONT>
