<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Amnesia is exremely useful in PvE.  If a cleric is gonna die I warn people about a second before I cast it.  It's not resisted that often, and casters know not to nuke immediately.  Tanks always get agro the next hit.  If you have trouble with it, it's your groups and not the spell.  I don't think I've ever gotten someone killed with it, and I use it often.  <P>In RvR I mostly use it against archers/Hibernians.  If I know I can't get into range to mez, I'll interupt their mez'ers as best I can.  It often gives our tanks just enough time to get on them.<P>--------------------<P>Ierar<BR>50 Sorcerer Bedevere<BR>40 Body/34 Mind
